message.body: Mm, okay. From this point on, I'll usually only be free on Fridays or the weekend.
Okay! Can i meet you on July 6th?
July 6th is good. What time? I'm busy from 3:00 and on.
I'm not sure because my class will have started then. I have not know what time my class will start..
That's all right. Just let me know whenever you find out.
